{
  "texts": [
    "The proposed VC(XGB+RF+ETC) ensemble model beat all competing learning models with accuracy, precision, recall, and F1 scores of 79.93%, 83.36%, and 84.67%, respectively.",
    "Individual machine learning models' overall performance while using the deleted missing value data is poor.",
    "The results of the machine learning model with deleted missing value data are represented graphically in Fig 3, which demonstrates that LR has the lowest accuracy scores.",
    "The model's performance is impacted by non-constant variation in the data.",
    "The performance of other models, aside from RF, ETC, XGBoost, and VC (XGB+RF+ETC), is average, according to the results."
  ]
}